OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1780344353
OL,3,CBiffa calls for vape disposal rules
OL,4,Cafter Aldridge fire
OL,6,FOne year on from the ban on the sale
OL,7,Fof single-use, non-refillable, or non-
OL,8,Frechargeable vapes, millions of the
OL,9,Frechargeable devices that replaced
OL,10,Fthem are being thrown away incorrectly.
OL,12,FAll vapes contain volatile lithium-ion
OL,13,Fbatteries, which can ignite when
OL,14,Fcrushed or damaged, posing a serious
OL,15,Frisk to waste workers, infrastructure
OL,16,Fand the public.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
