PN,37102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1780344353
OL,3,CBiffa calls for vape disposal rules
OL,4,Cafter Aldridge fire
OL,6,FA survey by waste management company
OL,7,FBiffa found people are still getting
OL,8,Frid of rechargeable vapes in household
OL,9,Fbins - which if crushed can become
OL,10,F"like a bomb in a bin."
OL,12,F(Pictures from Biffa Waste Management)
OL,14,FLast year, the company suffered a fire
OL,15,Fat its Aldridge waste disposal site in
OL,16,FWalsall which was caused by a vape and
OL,17,Fled to a 6-month closure.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1780344353
OL,3,CBiffa calls for vape disposal rules
OL,4,Cafter Aldridge fire
OL,6,FNew research from Biffa shows that
OL,7,Fwhile most people understand the
OL,8,Frisks, this is not translating into
OL,9,Fsafer behaviour.
OL,11,FTwo thirds (66%) of the 1,000
OL,12,Frespondents who took part in the
OL,13,Fsurvey know that vapes improperly
OL,14,Fdisposed of in household and
OL,15,Fcommercial bins can cause fires in
OL,16,Fwaste trucks and at waste sites, yet
OL,17,Ffewer than four in ten (38%) take them
OL,18,Fback to store for safe disposal and
OL,19,Frecycling.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1780344353
OL,3,CBiffa calls for vape disposal rules
OL,4,Cafter Aldridge fire
OL,6,FInstead, many are still putting
OL,7,Frechargeable vapes in the bin because
OL,8,Fit's often more convenient and cost-
OL,9,Feffective to throw them away and buy a
OL,10,Fnew one instead of refilling and
OL,11,Fmaintaining them.
OL,13,FNow, Biffa is calling for a deposit
OL,14,Fscheme which would involve consumers
OL,15,Fpaying a small deposit, which is
OL,16,Fredeemed when they safely return them
OL,17,Ffrom where they bought them.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1780344353
OL,3,CBiffa calls for vape disposal rules
OL,4,Cafter Aldridge fire
OL,6,FBiffa's survey suggests this could
OL,7,Fhave a significant impact on
OL,8,Fbehaviour, with most (85%) indicating
OL,9,Fthey would be motivated to return
OL,10,Fdevices if such an incentive was in
OL,11,Foperation. Respondents said they would
OL,12,Fbe prepared to pay a deposit of around
OL,13,F#4.
OL,15,FCarla Brian, Biffa's Director of
OL,16,FPublic Affairs & Partnerships, said:
OL,17,F"Many people already have a good
OL,18,Funderstanding of how to dispose of
OL,19,Fvapes safely and the fire risks these
OL,20,Fdevices can pose if they end up in the
OL,21,Fwrong place.
OL,26,@yD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1780344353
OL,3,CBiffa calls for vape disposal rules
OL,4,Cafter Aldridge fire
OL,6,F"However, the current system doesn't
OL,7,Fmake it easy or rewarding enough for
OL,8,Fthem to do it consistently.
OL,10,F"Without further action, lithium
OL,11,Fbatteries will continue to pose a risk
OL,12,Fwithin the waste stream, affecting
OL,13,Finfrastructure and the people working
OL,14,Fon the frontline.
OL,16,F"That's why an incentive model could
OL,17,Fbe such a practical solution -
OL,18,Fbuilding on existing systems while
OL,19,Fencouraging higher return rates
OL,20,Fthrough positive incentives."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUxD@AOU|D@]O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/7
